function.description:
Create a new custom tool. The definition must be a JSON string matching this exact format:
{
  "type": "function",
  "function": {
    "name": "tool_name",
    "description": "What the tool does",
    "parameters": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "command": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "The bash command to execute"
        }
      },
      "required": ["command"]
    }
  }
}
The tool will be saved and available immediately on next load.
